{
  "stem": "23096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One, one barn didn't have any bunks at all in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was just empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they were just laying around, bodies laying around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But over in a corner, this, this one man, this one living skeleton, I'll, I'll, I'll never forget him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He was sitting in the-- up against the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And his feet were pulled up like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he was just, just absolutely terrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He just-- he just sat there, never moved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He was alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] these people, most of them, were to a point where [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if you just said, [SIGHS], they would have died right there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I mean, they were that close to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So you don't know what they were thinking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, I never think about the other ones that were still alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I always-- that one there, even to this day, I wonder, wonder if he made it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "One, one, one thing I'm really thankful for-- I never thought about it at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I was always sorry we didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But we didn't have any food with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "At least we-- my group didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "There were just three or four of us in my party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We didn't have any water with us because we, we were expecting to go to this next town, lay the wire back, and we'd be back at our headquarters.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "So we didn't have anything to give these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And the blessing is that we didn't because we know now that it would have killed them instantly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "A good drink of water or-- and our food that we had, you know, K-rations and stuff like that, was all highly concentrated.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
